ack-routing/024-prefers-reduced-motion.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/07--cross-stack-routing/020-opencode-plus-motion-dev.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/07--cross-stack-routing/018-webflow-plus-motion-dev.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/02--language-sub-detection/005-opencode-python.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/01--surface-detection/002-opencode-detection.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/01--surface-detection/003-unknown-fallback.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/03--routing-disambiguation/009-skcode-vs-skdoc.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/02--language-sub-detection/004-opencode-typescript.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/05--motion-dev-and-animation-regression/014-animation-regression-baseline.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/06--cross-browser-and-performance-gates/015-cross-browser-animate.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/06--cross-browser-and-performance-gates/017-gpu-compositing.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual_testing_playbook/06--cross-browser-and-performance-gates/016-cwv-gates.md\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environme